reviewText: Dubbed off a VHS tape of a TV broadcast. Save your money and watch it on YouTube. Bootleg city.
If this is anything like the DVD its the sound track lifted from an old TV broadcast of Rockpalast via VCR tape. This is a bootleg and should be avoided.
This is a show that was taped  off an old TV broadcast on to VHS Tape. Poor quality and sound. Watch it on You Tube for superior picture and sound. Avoid!!!
Once again for someone who has made music for 37 years only Bob Dylan has that kind of longevity and quality
Taken From The German TV SHOW Rockpalast , , ELVIS COSTELLO AND THE ATTRACTIONS - WDR Studio-L Kln 15.06.1978
